name: The Alien of Catticus - Galactibles™ #19
description: Holy Catticus! Congratulations, you’ve discovered Galactible™ #19, the “Alien of Catticus!” The great alien race of Catticus has recognized you as an ally and has sent a representative to assist you with your travels through the Galactiverse! Becareful though, they can read your thoughts and only communicate telepathically. Your Mana has been raised by +4,000,000 bits! Custom music made by Pyramid Guy! Galactibles™ are one-of-a-kind and minted as 1-of-1. Only 99 will be made! New Galactibles™ drop every week (sorta) on twitter, so give us a follow @Galactibles! Certified authentic and original animations made by Pyramid Guy (IG: @pyramidguy), aka Kris Kanaly (TW: @kriskanaly). Galactibles™ ©2021 | galactibles.com
